Client --> SanatoriumBookingandContractsPlatform <<Relationship-UmVsYXRpb25zaGlw>> : "Registration, login, browse catalog, create and manage bookings\n<size:16>[HTTPS/REST]</size>"
Staff --> SanatoriumBookingandContractsPlatform <<Relationship-UmVsYXRpb25zaGlw>> : "Manage contracts, create/track payments, operational actions\n<size:16>[HTTPS/REST]</size>"

